		<tr>
			<td class="BoardRowB" colspan=3>
				As a roleplayer I more often than not dont group.. Its not that my charicters or myself are antisocial it that most of the times it seems hard to find some one to group with who understands why... My monk charicter never runs from a fight... <br> My ranger charicter never attacks wolves/bears or helps people in fights with them. <br> My dark elven rogue wont group with anyone other than Followers of the dark gods and refuses to speek common. <br>  <br> Does anyone else have problems like this and if not how do you deal with grouping with non roleplayers?		

